  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Step by Step - Promoting freedom of Expression and Press freedom in South Sudan.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project seeks to provide a free platform for South Sudanese citizens&#x2019; engagement in the peace process especially on the High Level Revitalization Forum (HLRF) and the Agreement on Resolution of Conflict as whole and other issues that pertain to peace building, democracy, good governance, freedom of expression and press freedom in South Sudan. The project will build on the work of an earlier project that was funded through CTP-FCO on &#x2018;&#x2019;Strengthening Peace, Democracy and Freedom of Expression in South Sudan&#x2019;&#x2019;. The project aims to create an enabling environment for journalists and citizens to express themselves freely. The project will continue with radio talk shows and dialogues that will focus on freedom of expression, peace building, trauma healing and reconciliation and the justice process. The activities shall be radio talk shows, dialogues, panel discussions, Vox Pops and public service announcements.</narrative>
  </description>
